9 FLOOR SUBSTITUTE
10 An Act relating to crimes and punishments; amending
Section 11, Chapter 366, O.S.L. 2024 (21 O.S. Supp.
11 2025, Section 20K), which relates to Class B6 felony
offenses; adding certain offense; updating statutory
12 references; amending 21 O.S. 2021, Section 51.1a,
which relates to second offense of first degree rape,
13 sodomy, lewd molestation, or sexual abuse of a child;
modifying certain sentencing provision; amending 21
14 O.S. 2021, Section 843.5, as last amended by Section
8, Chapter 486, O.S.L. 2025 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025,
15 Section 843.5), which relates to child abuse;
creating felony offense; providing penalties;
16 requiring certain advisement; defining terms;
updating statutory language; amending 22 O.S. 2021,
17 Section 991a, as last amended by Section 1, Chapter
306, O.S.L. 2025 (22 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 991a),
18 which relates to sentencing powers of the court;
modifying certain confinement criteria; requiring
19 electronic submission of certain report; updating
statutory references; and providing an effective
20 date.
21
22 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
23
