4 maliciously engage in enabling child neglect shall, upon conviction,
5 be guilty of a Class B1 felony offense and shall be punished by
6 imprisonment in the custody of the Department of Corrections not
7 exceeding life imprisonment, or by imprisonment in a county jail not
