4 c. procuring or causing the participation of a minor in
5 child pornography sexual abuse material, as provided
6 for in Section 1021.2 of this title,
7 d. purchase, procurement, or possession of child
8 pornography sexual abuse material, as provided for in
9 Section 1024.2 of this title,
10 e. engaging in or soliciting prostitution, as provided
11 for in Section 1029 of this title, if the offense
