1 c. penetration of the vagina or anus, however slight, by
2 an inanimate object or any part of the human body not
3 amounting to sexual intercourse,
4 d. sodomy, or
5 e. incest;
6 10. “Incest” means marrying, committing adultery, or
7 fornicating with a child by a person responsible for the health,
8 safety, or welfare of a child;
9 10. 11. “Lewd act or proposal” means:
10 a. making any oral, written, or electronic or computer-
